'''天主教卡坦杜瓦教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Catanduvensis}}；{{lang-pt|Diocese de Catanduva}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]一個[[天主教|天主教]][[教區|教區]]，位於[[聖保羅州|聖保羅州]]東北部，包括廿三市。此教區屬[[天主教里貝朗普雷圖總教區|里貝朗普雷圖總教區]]。

教區成立於2000年2月9日<ref>{{cite web |title=CATANDUVEN* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_20000209_venerabiles-frates.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-08-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825110734/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_20000209_venerabiles-frates.html |archivedate=2019-08-25 |language=la |date=2000-02-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年有教友212,735人，佔總人口77.3%。有三十個堂區、司鐸三十九人。現任教區主教為{{link-pt|瓦爾迪爾·馬梅德|Valdir Mamede}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 10.07.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/10/190710a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824180041/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/10/190710a.html |archivedate=2019-08-24 |language=en |date=2019-07-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-pt|安多尼·賽蘇·德-克羅茲|Antônio Celso de Queiroz|安多尼·賽蘇·克羅茲}}和{{link-pt|奧吉西利奧·盧西亞諾·達-席爾瓦|Otacílio Luziano da Silva}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE (CONTINUAZIONE), 21.10.2009 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/10/21/0654/01537.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825144200/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/10/21/0654/01537.html |archivedate=2019-08-25 |language=it |date=2009-10-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 10.10.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/10/10/181010c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825110420/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/10/10/181010c.html |archivedate=2019-08-25 |language=en |date=2018-10-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

